8143,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"好明顯佢好憎拿華斯"},{"pid":"4f636bb9ecada49e89f2672f09d23e2510266e90","tid":1086412,"uid":3798,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"C丹原來咁ON9<br />\n好在冇黎曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf9f9b0689f11361f5a6369a60dddd189315f7f","tid":1086412,"uid":3798,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6jwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=192be1fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】就盧卡施丹在周日西甲正選把關，皇家馬德里教練施丹認為愛兒在球隊年資不淺，具質素及個性。<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里周日以3:2險勝侯爾斯卡，賽後焦點之一顯然是施丹安排兒子盧卡施丹（Luca Zidane）正選把關，這安排或多或少令人意外，結果盧卡開賽3分鐘即失守。為此，施丹慈父上身維護愛兒。<br />\n<br />\n「我為他感到高興，因為那是他在班拿貝的地標戰，但他勝任球隊第3門將。」施丹賽後說：「泰拔（泰拔高圖爾斯）有傷，而經過為國家隊比賽後，我們想讓基羅拿華斯休息。」法國球王顯然想為兒子洗脫予人「新丁」的印象：「<span style=\"color: red;\">盧卡在皇家馬德里16年了</span>，之前一直在低組別比賽，但他具備質素與個性。」<br />\n<br />\n「我嘗試贏得所有比賽，但經過國際賽期後，我總想讓球員休息。」施丹也為輪換方針作出解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=25061987686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D25061987686&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6jwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=8099320d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=25061987686</a>"},{"pid":"6e153c004d9d09a80fecce1ed33439392a270610","tid":1086412,"uid":123410,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"990c47489df3035f5f0f38bbd50ae68a408f8173","tid":1086412,"uid":235174,"like":169,"dislike":3,"score":166,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/d3MM7Oev0ZMylznG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2Fd3MM7Oev0ZMylznG.gif&h=b4d0a522&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:57:3